jobInfo.postDescription:
Tasks and responsibilities：
- Check the Parts in the E-shopping cart and match the missing parts list and track part arrival status
- Install and connect the E-parts on the pre commissioning bench and do the pre commissioning
- Implement the version check, conduct version comparison with project requirements and documentation of the results and problems
- Implement the ECU software version update and documentation of the update results and problems
- Keys learning
- Coding, Parameterizing for the ECUs
- Calibrating of the sensors and actuators
- High voltage commissioning according to the protocol, include high voltage system equipotential and insulation resistance detection, Insulation fault simulation detection…
- Static and dynamic vehicle function test according to the function list and documentation of the results and problems
- Function problems and ECU errors analysis, clarification with R&D departments, elimination and documentation in the problem list.
- Acquisition of the deviation description for the electric problems and errors from R&D departments
- Do the commissioning rework according to Quality department’s requirements and guarantee the car’s ZP8 from commissioning site
- Summary and preparation of project’s commissioning guidance documents
 Qualification：
- At least 2 years’ experience in commissioning or EE Integration Testing
- Knowledge about CAN bus and CANoe Tool
- Degree in mechanical engineering, automotive engineering, electrical engineering, industrial engineering, computer science or equivalent qualifications 
- Chinese & English speaking
- Good communication ability, executive ability, team player
- Structured working methods, high dedication, high degree of initiative, assertiveness
jobInfo.address: 合肥蜀山区大众汽车(安徽)有限公司安徽大众

brandComInfo.introduce:
in-tech GmbH 是一家德国工程服务公司。为汽车、工业和运输行业的数字化、自动化和开发提供支持。公司在德国、奥地利、美国、墨西哥、中国、捷克共和国、英国和罗马尼亚设有分公司，提供全面的产品和服务组合。我们成立于 2002 年，目前在十个国家/地区的20个地点拥有超过 2,100名高资质工程师。稳健的盈利和快速的成长速度使我们拥有独特的企业文化：包容且富有激情。

我们为各行业提供多种解决方案，包括系统整合、研发、测试验证和技术咨询。以汽车行业为例，从产品的需求管理、架构设计、功能研发、硬件及软件开发，到功能验证及测试、整车测试、缺陷分析等，我们都有专业的工程团队提供高效且严谨的服务。在汽车信息娱乐系统、自动驾驶、动力总成、底盘、NVH、新能源电池及充电应用、数据中心等领域均有强大的团队进行支持。

除了专业的工程团队外，公司的orange系列产品可以使汽车系统的测试更加高效、准确和可靠。例如，orangeSwitch 自动切换系统可在电子控制单元 (ECU) 测试之间自动切换，为汽车 ECU 控制系统提供更高效的测试台。orangeSwitch 允许自动从 ECU 控制系统的一个实时虚拟仿真切换到另一个仿真，无需人工干预，允许在非工作时间进行测试，同时支持所有常见的测试自动化框架。

欲了解更多信息，欢迎访问我们的官方网站 www.in-tech.com
